org.cloudbus.cloudsim

Class VmScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.VmScheduler
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    VmSchedulerSpaceShared, VmSchedulerTimeShared

    public abstract class VmScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
    VmScheduler is an abstract class that represents the policy used by a VMM to share processing power among VMs running in a host.
    Since:
    CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
